parameters: Guhah! Who the hell are you!
Esuka! Wasn't the plan to act covertly!?

It's okay. I won't even give them time to scream,
so that's covert, right?
Is, is this guy a cyborg!

So you're the rumored Resistance! Perfect, I'll
take you down and get a bonus!
Oh? You're not running away, that helps.

The sweep is complete. Now, onto the secret
mission.

You're misunderstanding the meaning of your words.
Seriously, we need to retreat soon.

My name is Shuu. I'm a part of the resistance,
fighting against the oppression of the Imperial
Army. Today, I was supposed to be conducting
covert operations in the city to gather some
information, but...

Ah, thank you... Could it be, you're the
Resistance? So you really do exist...

...We should leave this place soon. The Imperial
Army will probably be back before long.

This is my buddy, Esuka. She was once attacked by
the Imperial Army and suffered near-fatal
injuries. Now, she's a cyborg with over 90% of her
body mechanized. Her body, adjusted for combat,
doesn't get hurt easily.

That being said, she is equipped with functions
that serve as a substitute for sensory nerves,
allowing her to live a human-like life. She should
feel pain when injured, but she doesn't seem to
care and often acts recklessly, which is a cause
for concern.

Well, as the operator, it's my job to control her,
so it could be said that it's due to my lack of
power....

The thought of them laying a hand on even a child
makes me sick.

Speaking of which, you mentioned something about
an auction... as for that merchandise.

Yes, it seems the information about the auction
day approaching is correct.

Don't get carried away. However, there might be
guys looking for the merchandise nearby, just like
earlier.

That's right! It seems like there's not much time
until the auction, so let's beat up a few more
people and gather information!

Right now, we are gathering information about the
human trafficking auctions that are regularly held
in the empire. Of course, our goal is to stop
them, but we also aim to expose their true nature
to international public opinion and heighten the
momentum against the empire.

※There will be choices after this. Do you want to
save? (Depending on your choice, it may result in
a game over)
Alright, I'm counting on you to be careful.
No, we should retreat for now.

Why?! The auction is soon, right⁉ We should
hurry...

That's true. But if they're still gathering prizes
now, it probably won't happen today or tomorrow.
Let's prepare thoroughly and try again.
Hey, hey~ It's time to pay your taxes~!

Please, have mercy! Didn't we just pay last week?
At this rate, we'll have nothing left to wear or
eat.

No problem, if that's the case, we'll just
conscript your brats instead.
Ahhh! Please, I beg you, anything but that!

Shut up! We need goods for the auction! What will
happen if we don't meet our quota? Our bonuses
will be cut!
That's too much! I'll take their place instead!

Shut up! Do you dare to argue with an Imperial
soldier? Unforgivable! It's a death sentence!
